title: Maren Morris On Getting To Meet One of Her Favorite Celebs and New Music  + Lunchbox Calls To Try and Get A Babysitter for Himself + A Caller Has A Question About How Music on the Radio Works
itunes:title: Maren Morris On Getting To Meet One of Her Favorite Celebs and New Music  + Lunchbox Calls To Try and Get A Babysitter for Himself + A Caller Has A Question About How Music on the Radio Works
description:
We talk to our friend, Maren Morris. She tells us about her new song out today, how she hopes to not fall on stage this year and the story behind the picture on her Instagram with her and Amy Poehler. Lunchbox prank calls a day care center and tries to get a babysitter for himself, not a child. A caller has a question for Bobby about a song he heard on the radio…but now doesn’t anymore and wants to know how songs on the radio work.
